<pb facs="1063884" n="1"/>
<note>1714 Aug. 3</note>
<opener>
<lb/>Vir Doctissime, et Celeberrime</opener>
<p><lb/>Ex iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in <rs key="B_991170515020205501" type="letter">litteris</rs> incomparabilis Patrui tui <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nis</rs> 18<hi rend="sup">a</hi> Julii datis, nec non ex postrema tua <rs key="B_991170517053705501" type="letter">episto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>la</rs> mihi valde grata, rationes percepi ob quas respon<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs key="B_991170517053905501" type="letter">litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> 15.<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <choice><sic>Maj</sic><corr>Maij</corr></choice> ad me miss<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> neutiquam ad
         <lb/>meas perven<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>re manus. Cursorum negligentia, vel lites
         <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> inter vestros postarum directores et Mediolanenses
         <lb/>intercedunt fortasse in causa fuerunt ut ego frustra expec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>taverim di<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice> tuas et Patrui tui epistolas. Impraesen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiarum mihi plurimum gaudeo postquam ex hac
            <lb/>ultima tua <rs key="B_991170517053705501" type="letter">epistola</rs> intellexi te optima frui vale<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tudine, et me amare (quod mihi iucundissimum est) per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gere.</p>
<p><lb/>Ex meis <rs key="B_991170515020005501" type="letter">litteris</rs> <del>ad</del>hac die ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> tuum, inter
         <lb/>omnes Mathematicos primas merentem, missis intel<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>liges quid pro ipso et pro Te Vir Clarissime praestare
            <lb/>potuerim apud istos Nobiliss<hi rend="sup">os</hi>. <rs type="organisation"><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavini</rs> Archilyc<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>i</rs>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatores</rs>. Si <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> tuus Illustrissimus Stipendium
         <lb/>annuum recuset <del><unclear>15</unclear></del>1200 florenorum italorum cum
            <lb/>annexis conditionibus docendi per triennium <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavij</rs>
<lb/>poste<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te eiusdem loco substituendi ita ut ipse possit
            <lb/>in <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Patriam</rs> redire post tres annos te remanente
         <lb/>Patavii, rem pro te f<unclear>e</unclear>re desperatam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>video.
            <lb/>Etenim tui promotio<subst><del><gap/></del><add>nunc</add></subst> nunc dependet <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Doctissimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs>
<lb/>tuo; quem ita magni faciunt <abbr>Illus.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Mo<pc type="hyphenation">
</pc><lb break="no"/>
<pb facs="1063886" n="2"/>deratores</rs> ut cum sint vocaturi salario, quod hactenus
         <lb/>nemini ex Professoribus scientias quascunque etiam Ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>thematicas <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> docentibus fuit propositum. Uti in
   <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentibus meis <rs key="B_991170517053705501" type="letter">Litteris</rs> admonui maxima Patrui
         <lb/>fama non leve adfert tibi dam num in hoc negotio.
         <lb/>Obsecra igitur nomine meo Vir Clarissime per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>eximium <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> tuum ut Provinciam <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavi</rs> <pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nam salario memorato 1200 florenorum italo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum, amplectatur: hac enim incede<subst><del><gap/></del><add><unclear>nda</unclear></add></subst> via post
         <lb/>tres annos plus minus tu certissime promoveberis
            <lb/>cum honorifico stipendio. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> tuus paucis cum ex<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pensis poterit vivere <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs>, et toto vacationum
         <lb/>tempore in domo mea habitare summo cum meo
         <lb/>honore poterit gratis, mihique rem plurimum gra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tam faciet.</p>
<p><lb/>Statim ac accepero <rs key="biblio_WPXENY2H biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_RTB4565Q" type="biblio">fasciculum</rs> librorum mittendo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergomum</rs> ad <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> et <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">um</hi>.</abbr> <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr> Comi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089631200" type="person">Carolum Zenobium</rs>, <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517053705501">litteras</rs> tuas contentas
   <lb/><rs key="biblio_69NKSR46" type="biblio">libro</rs> cui titulus <hi rend="u"><foreign xml:lang="fre">Essai d’Analyse sur les <choice><orig>ieux</orig><reg>jeux</reg></choice>
<lb/>de hazard</foreign></hi> ostendam loco speciminis nobilissimis
         <lb/>hisce Moderatoribus, quorum voluntas est ut ad<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>veniat saltem pro tribus annis Celeberrimus
          <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> tuus, cui post e<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te libenter substi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><pb facs="1063887" n="3"/>
            tuent. Iidem (si ipse venire non recusabit) scribent, spe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro, <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> ad Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi> vestrum <rs type="person">Magistratum</rs>,<del> ut</del>
<lb/>et rogabunt ut permittat eiusdem adventum sal<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem per triennium.</p>
<p><lb/>Ipse Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> tuus profect<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> <choice><sic>m<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>retur</sic><corr>meretur</corr></choice> etiam
         <lb/>plus quam 1500 Thaleros imperiales pro quolibet anno
         <lb/>si ad illius mentem incomparabilem respiciamus:
         <lb/>ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m huiusmodi stipendium nunquam accipiet ab
            <lb/>hac Sereniss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi> et Potentiss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Republica</rs>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> eximios Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fessores cuiuscunque scienti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> solet promovere
         <lb/>primo triennio salario 400, 500, aut 600 flo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>renorum italorum crescendo postea quolibet trien<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nio, si Professores rite sua munia obierint. Ingenue
         <lb/>fateor et testor nemini fuisse primo triennio exhi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bitum salarium 900, 1000, aut 1200 florenorum Ita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lorum.</p>
<p><lb/>Responsum a Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> hac super re expecta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bo quamprimum. Quod si ipse <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Patria</rs> vestra disce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dere nolet <del>,</del> etiam salario, et conditionibus supradictis
         <lb/>sibi propositis; ego aliquid pro Te pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stare, si pote<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro, non desinam, licet mea officia inutilia praevi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>deam. Tu interim me<subst><del>a</del><add>u</add></subst>m animum tibi maxime ad<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dictum accepta, sciasque me semper futurum fo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re ad mandata tua paratissimum.</p> <closer>Vale et
                <pb facs="1063888" n="4"/>
<lb/>amare non desine
                  <lb/><subst><del>Tui</del><add>Magni</add></subst> Tui Nominis
   <lb/><note type="editorial">Original steht die dateline vor dieser Zeile.</note>Cultorem Studiosissimum et
         <lb/>Observantissimum
                  <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrum Antonium Michelotti</rs>.</closer>
   <lb/><dateline><rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <abbr>a. d. </abbr><date when="1714-08-03">3 Augusti MDCCXIV</date>.</dateline>
